    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Inkle"><a href="#Inkle" class="headerlink" title=" Inkle"></a><center> Inkle</h1><img src="/img/my/04/inkle-black.png" style="zoom:20%" /><p>关于Inkle<sup id="fnref:1" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="Inkle[inkle官网]: https://www.inklestudios.com/[inkle资料]: https://www.inklestudios.com/press/[Inky快速入门]: https://www.yuque.com/inky/pcke0w/gix3ga[Inky下载渠道]: https://github.com/inkle/inky[Writing with ink]: https://github.com/inkle/ink/blob/master/Documentation/WritingWithInk.md[Inky游戏列表]: https://github.com/inkle/ink-library[inklewriter]: https://www.inklewriter.com/">[1]</span></a></sup>  </p><p>inkle 由两位剑桥游戏开发商于2011年创立，他们对讲故事和精美的设计充满热情。<br>ink 是一门围绕标记纯文本展开的脚本语言，以生成互动脚本。<br>Inky 则是一个编辑器,是以英国剑桥的一只黑猫命名。<br>inklewriter 是ink的在线编辑器。</p><h2 id="Inky-小故事"><a href="#Inky-小故事" class="headerlink" title="Inky 小故事"></a>Inky 小故事</h2><h3 id="一个例子"><a href="#一个例子" class="headerlink" title="一个例子"></a>一个例子</h3><iframe src="https://inky-example.netlify.app/" width="100%" height="700" name="topFrame" scrolling="yes"  noresize="noresize" frameborder="0" id="topFrame"></iframe><h2 id="Link"><a href="#Link" class="headerlink" title="Link"></a>Link</h2><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>Inkle<br>[inkle官网]: <a href="https://www.inklestudios.com/">https://www.inklestudios.com/</a><br>[inkle资料]: <a href="https://www.inklestudios.com/press/">https://www.inklestudios.com/press/</a><br>[Inky快速入门]: <a href="https://www.yuque.com/inky/pcke0w/gix3ga">https://www.yuque.com/inky/pcke0w/gix3ga</a><br>[Inky下载渠道]: <a href="https://github.com/inkle/inky">https://github.com/inkle/inky</a><br>[Writing with ink]: <a href="https://github.com/inkle/ink/